OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775927152
OL,3,CHealthcare recruitment company says
OL,4,Cgardai probing 'cyber security
OL,5,Cincident'
OL,7,FA healthcare recruitment company
OL,8,Fworking on the island of Ireland has
OL,9,Fsaid it was "the victim of a cyber
OL,10,Fsecurity incident".
OL,12,FHealthdaq said the incident has been
OL,13,Freported to the relevant regulatory
OL,14,Fand law enforcement authorities
OL,15,Fincluding the Garda National Cyber
OL,16,FCrime Bureau.
OL,26,@qD@MOUrD@RO]
