OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775927152
OL,3,CHealthcare recruitment company says
OL,4,Cgardai probing 'cyber security
OL,5,Cincident'
OL,7,FThe company states that it works with
OL,8,Fhealth and social care trusts and the
OL,9,FDepartment of Health in Northern
OL,10,FIreland and has listed a Dublin-based
OL,11,Fdisability service provider as a
OL,12,Fclient.
OL,14,FHealthdaq, which has offices in
OL,15,FBelfast and Dublin, said in a
OL,16,Fstatement: "As this incident is the
OL,17,Fsubject of an active criminal
OL,18,Finvestigation, we cannot make any
OL,19,Ffurther comments at this time."
OL,26,@xD@LOU{D@_O]
